  "title": "TAILOR'S CUTTER",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Take accurate body measurements for custom-made garments</p></li><li><p>Draft, adjust, and prepare cutting patterns</p></li><li><p>Cut fabrics precisely according to design and measurements</p></li><li><p>Work closely with tailors and designers to ensure perfect fit and quality</p></li><li><p>Minimise fabric wastage and maintain cutting tools</p></li><li><p>Ensure work meets company quality standards and deadlines</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a tailor’s cutter</p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of fabrics, patterns, and cutting techniques</p></li><li><p>Ability to read and understand garment designs</p></li><li><p>Attention to detail and good workmanship</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Responsible, hardworking, and reliable</p></li></ul>",
